\c 14
\s Jehovha anodana Israeri kuti vadzokere kwaari
\p
\v 1 Aiwa, imwi Israeri, dzokerai kuna Jehovha Mwari wenyu, nokuti makagumburwa nezvakaipa zvenyu.
\v 2 Endai namashoko, mudzokere kuna Jehovha, muti kwaari, Bvisai zvakaipa zvose, mugamuchire zvinhu zvakanaka, ipapo tichakupai miromo yedu, zvive zvibairo zvedu.
\v 3 Asiriya havangatiponesi; hatingatasvi mabhiza, hatingazoti kubasa ramaoko edu. Ndimi vamwari vedu; nokuti nherera dzinowana nyasha kwamuri.
\v 4 Ndichaporesa kudzokera kwavo shure, ndichavada nokuda kwangu; nokuti kutsamwa kwangu kwabviswa kwavari.
\v 5 Ndichava sedova kuna Israeri, vachatunga seruva, vachatanda midzi yavo seRebhanoni.
\v 6 Matavi avo achatanda, kunaka kwavo kuchafanana nomuorivhi, nokunhuhwira kwavo sokweRebhanoni.
\p
\v 7 Vanogara mumumvuri wavo vachadzoka, vachavandudzika sezviyo, nokutunga maruva somuzambiringa; kurumbidzwa kwavo kuchafanana newaini yeRebhanoni.
\p
\v 8 Efuremu, ndichineiko nezvifananidzo? Ndakapindura, ndinehanya naye; ndakafanana nomuonde mutema, zvibereko zvako zvichawanikwa kwandiri.
\p
\v 9 Ndianiko akachenjera, anzwisise zvinhu izvi, kana akangwara, azvizive? Nokuti nzira dzaJehovha dzakarurama, vakarurama vachafamba nadzo; asi vadariki vachawa madziri.
